description:
{SET OF SIX}

Happy happy birds singing in the trees – an original illustration letterpress printed on thick eco-friendly 100% cotton cards.

Six flat notes (with matching burnt-orange envelopes) printed with care on a hand-fed Chandler & Price Old Style letterpress by Sweet Olive Press in Colorado.

Choose these letterpress notes as a delightful gift, or keep them for yourself –- they're perfect for sending warm thoughts to an old friend! 

Notecard measurements: 5.5in x 4.25in

{all images and artwork copyright sweet olive press, all rights reserved}

{SET OF FIVE}

Charming songbirds on a branch – original artwork letterpress printed on luxurious 100% cotton cards.

These cards were printed one by one on a 108-year-old Chandler & Price Old Style letterpress, using a magnesium plate made from my original line drawing.

Five cards (measurements: 5.5in x 4.25in) packaged in a clear resealable sleeve with recycled envelopes in dusty rose.

The distinctive paper I use is made from 100% reclaimed cotton – so materials that would otherwise be destined for the landfills are instead used to create the beautiful stock for your cards!

{all images and artwork copyright 2010 sweet olive press}

{SET OF SIX}

A dreamy silver moon and stars hang from the top of these notes – an original design letterpress printed on rich 100% cotton (tree-free!) stock.

Six A2 flat cards printed with care using magnesium plates and hand-mixed inks on a hand-fed Chandler & Price Old Style letterpress by Sweet Olive Press in Colorado. Packaged with pool blue envelopes.

Card measurements: 5.5in x 4.25in

{all images and artwork copyright sweet olive press, all rights reserved}

{SET OF SIX}

A fabulous vintage mod girl image letterpress printed on rich 100% cotton cards in a "brushed metal" shade of hand-mixed ink. 

Six A2 flat cards printed with care on a hand-fed Chandler & Price Old Style letterpress, and packaged with silver envelopes. 

Card measurements: 5.5in x 4.25in

{all images and artwork copyright sweet olive press, all rights reserved}
